    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Service_Amazon_Ec2_Ebs::createVolumeFromSnapshot() shall accept third optional parameter "size". Without it it's impossible to implement this resizing mechanism, for example: <a href="http://blog.edoceo.com/2009/02/amazon-ebs-how-to-grow-storage.html">http://blog.edoceo.com/2009/02/…</a></p>

<p>As Amazon specification says this param is acceptable: <a href="http://docs.amazonwebservices.com/AWSEC2/latest/CommandLineReference/index.html?ApiReference-cmd-CreateVolume.html">http://docs.amazonwebservices.com/AWSEC2/latest/…</a></p>

